{"tid":502423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[耆靈王]大埔老人院兩老打架一死，警方列謀殺案處理","createTime":"2017-12-18T01:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T02:32:24.000Z","uid":22575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9543449c04daa3161aedf5e4fe35442771e94cb0","tid":502423,"uid":22575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大埔發生命案。現場為舊墟直街22至28號一間老人院，早上6時許，職員發現有一名老翁昏迷，於是報警，由救護車送院搶救，最終不治。<br />\n<br />\n調查期間，警方發現死者較早前曾與院內另一名老翁打架，懷疑對方與案件有關，隨即將他拘捕，列作謀殺案跟進。</span>"},{"pid":"08149a5c61734adf4489cac885082db587787d8d","tid":502423,"uid":100230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T02:27:25.000Z","msg":"老當益葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541c2ef910b6a5cd546387401f70b50e8602880e","tid":502423,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 耆靈王"},{"pid":"8bbf4b4d3f7c6054be02e08114d847de055ddb26","tid":502423,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"第一屆全港耆英綜合格鬥比賽現正開始"}]}